    a simple UI. use ADD to add a maneuver, set the\nposition and RSW components
    (radial, in-track, cross-track). Use \nADD to add more than one maneuver then
    execute. \n\nController code is described in more detail in docs."
  url: https://nbodyphysics.com/ge2/html/tutorial_MultipleMan.html
